@baseUrl = http://localhost:18000
@keyword = Laptop
@invalidToken = invalid.jwt.token

### Search tenant-scoped master data through Kong
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-demo-001

### Missing token should return 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
X-Request-Id: search-demo-missing-token

### Invalid token should return 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
Authorization: Bearer {{invalidToken}}
X-Request-Id: search-demo-invalid-token

### Blank keyword should return 400 after authentication
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/master-data?keyword=
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-demo-blank-keyword
